entries.femaleVariant: Must be V. My chauffeur.
Alois Daquin?
Escort. Not chauffeur.
Alois Daquin?
Escort. Not chauffeur. Everything else, yeah.
My, with a penetrating mind like that, you will get far. Yes, Alois Daquin.
Whatever you want. All I need is for you to get me out of this shithole.
Yeah, let's go.
C'mon.
I can't wait.
Goddamn Night City... I won't miss it.
Over there. Meeting spot with the nomads. Stop the car.
Raffens should be here soon. Can't let them see you here with me.
Raffens? We've met before. You sure about this?
You waiting for something? Your job's done.
I'm not... Hm, OK â€“ let's say a few bad loans, taken out to cover a very high-risk investment.
Distributing experimental supplements under the aegis of Night Corp's humanitarian aid division.
Supplements, hah. You mean...
Not vitamins, no. Besides, doesn't matter. All went south. Fucked me sideways, but my debts stayed put.
Fucking Night City! Draws you in with its promises, offers you endless options on a silver platter, and then... Then it just lops your wings right off.
Come on, Daquin. Be honest.
What're you running from?
Better than staying in town. But thanks for your concern.
Watch it, Daquin. I start tearing up, we don't go anywhere.
Fine, just... Just get me out of here.
I'm parked nearby. We going?
